  <thing id="rcEMPRapHC" name="Hawk Clan" description="Members of your clan resemble hawks when using their change shape ability. You gain a +2 racial bonus to Wisdom. Whenever you gain an inquisitor level, if you would normally gain a bonus feat from the teamwork feat class feature on that class level, you may instead choose to gain the Raptor Clan Heritage feat as a bonus feat. You cannot use the teamwork feat class feature to replace Raptor Clan Heritage with a teamwork feat, or vice versa." compset="RaceCustom" summary="Appear as a hawk when you shapechange, gain heritage as inquistor." uniqueness="useronce">
